#bold[#magenta[Synopsis:]] steroids emulate #bold[mode] #cyan[--options]

  Launches the iOS Simulator or Android Emulator

#bold[#magenta[Available modes and options:]]

  #bold[ios]          Starts the iOS Simulator (OS X only)
    #cyan[--devices]
      Lists all supported devices and SDKs

    #cyan[--device=<type>]
    #cyan[--device=<type>@<sdk>]
      #bold[type] See: #cyan[--devices]
      #bold[sdk]  The iOS SDK version e.g. iPhone-6@8.1 ... assuming that it is installed